Five\
 \uc0\u8232 Heaven and Earth are impartial; \u8232 They see the ten thousand things as straw dogs. \u8232 The wise are impartial; \u8232 They see the people as straw dogs. \u8232 The space between heaven and Earth is like a bellows. \u8232 The shape changes but not the form; \u8232 The more it moves, the more it yields. \u8232 More words count less. \u8232 Hold fast to the center.\
\'a0\
\uc0\u8232 \
